Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["Logistic regression (classification)", "Chapter",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781682664563157*^9, 
  3.7816826758682165`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2f76e6cd-67a3-4433-abcb-\
071480538a7b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Logistic regression is a classification method.\n\nIn its simplest version, \
it is designed to classify into two classes, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["C", "1"], ",", 
      SubscriptBox["C", "2"]}], "}"}], "."}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"c2033c71-1df5-42e8-81b4-9dee61f027aa"]
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7817012204354887`*^9, 
  3.7817013568385096`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1753b18c-8d9e-4ca2-9508-\
84b8b106ed49"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Features:",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " Suppose that we have a data set in which instances are characterised by ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["M", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "3d372bd3-a18b-428e-b997-d1ad231041dd"],
 " numerical features: ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    StyleBox["x",
     FontWeight->"Bold"], " ", "=", " "}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "fcf18fdf-c44e-4e0e-8d75-49e5e8a6789c"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["x", "1"], ",", 
     SubscriptBox["x", "2"], ",", "...", ",", 
     SubscriptBox["x", "M"]}], "}"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "56174446-fe4e-444e-a11f-86c74fa36a89"],
 "\n\n",
 StyleBox["Dependent variable:",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " The class of examples are given by a ",
 StyleBox["binary variable ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"y", "=", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{"0", ",", "1"}], "}"}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"9be2f550-c67e-49f0-b127-1fe073ff601c"],
 "  (",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["C", "1"], " ", "for", " ", "y"}], "=", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"0", " ", "and", " ", 
       SubscriptBox["C", "2"], " ", "for", " ", "y"}], "=", "1"}]}], ")"}], 
   TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->"d74e575c-97c6-478b-bbe3-55da15aa5604"],
 ".\n\n",
 StyleBox["Aim:",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " Given an unseen example with feature vector ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    StyleBox["x",
     FontWeight->"Bold"], "'"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "aa49ab71-bc59-47e7-a995-31a8cd5c99bc"],
 ", we want to predict the value of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["y", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "f1f4d8e9-5307-4e3d-bc45-4ded58b8027a"],
 ", i.e. the class of the unseen example."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.7817023466608906`*^9, {3.781702591768141*^9, 3.7817027035190954`*^9}, {
   3.781702831535224*^9, 3.781702870548295*^9}, 
   3.78211237589363*^9},ExpressionUUID->"0db6bcc0-488d-435d-889d-\
d13d0213cc46"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Example: Menarche as a function of age", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7817013645896845`*^9, 3.781701423573084*^9}, {
  3.7817255686946917`*^9, 
  3.7817255779193764`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"afb8843b-5d05-458d-9b0d-\
3b7b8d21695a"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Aim", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7817015194851575`*^9, 
  3.7817015199672055`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"9e56ba39-8a13-4457-a095-\
9ca4016600f1"],

Cell["\<\
To motivate the functioning of logistic regression, we address the following \
problem: Predict whether or not a girl will have had her first period \
(menarche) at a certain age.

In order to do that, we use data to train a classifier that uses logistic \
regression as a method.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7817015248548727`*^9, 3.781701685108961*^9}, {
  3.7817028968418617`*^9, 3.781702915729927*^9}, {3.781703156652603*^9, 
  3.781703178276752*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"9b2742e7-022e-45be-81f9-\
b9de56e7bcc9"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["The data", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781701513266593*^9, 
  3.7817015143132095`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f9db45b2-6751-4033-895b-\
e8ad1dbb6d53"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Description",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "\nThe juul data frame has 1339 rows and 6 columns. It contains a reference \
sample of the distribution of insulin-like growth factor (IGF-I), one \
observation per subject in various ages, with the bulk of the data collected \
in connection with school physical examinations.\n\n",
 StyleBox["Format",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "\n\nThis data frame contains the following columns:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781690999703145*^9, 3.7816910379674745`*^9}, {
  3.781701750437681*^9, 
  3.781701753428906*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f91bb900-d8fb-4848-be1e-\
6a4ed4a98012"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["age - a numeric vector (years).  - ",
  FontColor->RGBColor[0, 0, 1]],
 StyleBox["Feature ",
  FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, 0]],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   StyleBox["x",
    FontWeight->"Bold"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, 0],ExpressionUUID->
  "ca56dedc-f585-45ae-ac94-921aba6f9b3b"],
 StyleBox[" in our analysis",
  FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, 0]]
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7816910512830906`*^9, 3.7816910530778065`*^9}, {
  3.7817031823328686`*^9, 
  3.781703215145485*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3647d9c1-4c2f-48e9-b88d-\
2ee7efb6d8fe"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["menarche - a numeric vector. Has menarche occurred (code 1: no, 2: \
yes)? - ",
  FontColor->RGBColor[0, 0, 1]],
 StyleBox["Dependent variable ",
  FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, 0]],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["y", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "80511155-13ec-4e4e-8522-8714bbec8710"]
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7816910512830906`*^9, 3.7816910604803314`*^9}, {
  3.781703212235958*^9, 
  3.7817032532088995`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e35c0b3d-8029-488d-9609-\
e2fa9fc2d108"],

Cell["sex -a numeric vector (1: boy, 2: girl).", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7816910512830906`*^9, 
  3.7816910676802497`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"08457468-0193-4dc7-890d-\
761882ba9b3a"],

Cell["\<\
igf1 - a numeric vector, insulin-like growth factor (microgram per liter).\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7816910512830906`*^9, 
  3.781691074810357*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0d9962e5-bc0d-414f-a677-\
78bda79f339e"],

Cell["\<\
tanner - a numeric vector, codes 1\[Dash]5: Stages of puberty ad modum Tanner.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7816910512830906`*^9, 
  3.781691080572317*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5cef0a14-a1fa-4f9c-a95b-\
3eec1f585deb"],

Cell["testvol - a numeric vector, testicular volume (ml).", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7816910512830906`*^9, 
  3.781691086209547*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"fedfe5dd-296c-44d6-830b-\
204713088081"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Source",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "\nThe data contains variables from an investigation performed by Anders \
Juul (Rigshospitalet, Department for Growth and Reproduction, Denmark)\n\
Presented in the following book:\nPeter Dalgaard, \"Introductory Statistics \
with R\", 2nd Edition, Springer (2008). \nData available in the 'ISwR' R \
package."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781690999703145*^9, 3.781691017684683*^9}, {
  3.7816910930774107`*^9, 3.7816911065539956`*^9}, {3.781701759323848*^9, 
  3.781701775041989*^9}, {3.781701860777678*^9, 
  3.7817019799072266`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"42cda892-76f0-4c0d-b66d-\
bc91083d2168"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Selecting the feature (age) and dependent variable (menarche) \
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781703279218868*^9, 
  3.781703307523939*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"72f97a49-4ac2-4253-9bec-\
660baaca5ece"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Download the data ",
 StyleBox["juul.dat", "CodeText"],
 " from MyAberdeen and import it (remember that you can use Insert -> File \
path... to find the data file in your local directory)"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781702941690935*^9, 3.7817029423920603`*^9}, {
  3.781702976746564*^9, 3.781702993934533*^9}, {3.781703313891119*^9, 
  3.7817033142943153`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1a9dcb2c-356d-41b6-9b55-\
1ff530d0db07"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"juul", "=", 
   RowBox[{
   "Import", "[", 
    "\"\<H:\\\\Teaching\\\\MSc_Data_Science\\\\2022-2023_II\\\\Data\\\\juul.\
dat\>\"", "]"}]}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7816906666750455`*^9, 3.7816906758341384`*^9}, {
   3.7816907313692465`*^9, 3.7816907333401194`*^9}, 3.7816907852550793`*^9, {
   3.907054316164013*^9, 3.9070543511969852`*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[1]:=",ExpressionUUID->"4a91a4a1-d2bf-4926-b096-efd49b2fe2f2"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"Take", "[", 
  RowBox[{"juul", ",", "10"}], "]"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7817030807925787`*^9, 3.7817030867024655`*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[2]:=",ExpressionUUID->"096a8d40-0f9f-4bd0-8850-37ca875135ee"],

